  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Genjutsu (Phantasm)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 7 (Spell Level 4)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 8</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 22 | <b>Successes:</b> 4</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 10 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 24</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You send powerful and disturbing visions to disturb the target's rest. The subject suffers 1d10 damage and does not benefit from a night's rest as they normally would. The subject will become fatigued and be unable to naturally recover hit points or Chakra for one day.<br><br>The target may receive a bonus or penalty to their save based on how well you know them. If you know nothing about the target, they gain a +10 bonus. If you have some second-hand knowledge, they gain a +5 bonus. If you are intimately familiar with them, they suffer a -5 penalty.<br><br>This technique cannot be dispelled, and cannot be used on a creature more than once per week.</p>\n\n\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
